member.name: T:SmartFran.Seed.Logging.ILogger
member.summary:
Common contract for trace instrumentation. You can implement this contrat with several frameworks. .NET Diagnostics API, EntLib, Log4Net,NLog etc.
The use of this abstraction depends on the real needs you have and the specific features you want to use of a particular existing implementation. You could also eliminate this abstraction and directly use "any" implementation in your code, LoggerFactory.Write(new LogEntry()) in EntLib, or LogManager.GetLog("logger-name") with log4net... etc.
